New tools for the expertise of cars
In these days of storms and accidents, not only earn the car garages.
Every day, thousands of cars that have suffered a sinister are towed to a garage, where an expert must assess the damage and the cost of the repair.
No sinister is equal, and the calculation of the cost of the parts and labor time can be a long and complex task.
Calculate the cost of the repair of between 20,000 and 30,000 euros, including parts and labor, can take two or three hours.
However, with the support of the latest computer tools, it would be a matter of minutes.
That is why almost 100% of the experts use this type of systems.
The suppliers of services and solutions for the assessment of claims and maintenance are dedicated to the collection of information provided by the manufacturers, and then to treat them and offer their customers in the form of a useful tool.
In Spain, Audatex, part of the American group, is the company leader; 80% of the estimates are made with its products.
The other companies that compete in the field of tools and the development of information on the sector, are gtmotive and Eurotax.
